latestPosts.caption:
TTRN 2025 – A moment etched in my heart.
Walking the ramp in this beautifully crafted lehenga by the incredibly talented designer Kanak Thakur was an absolute honor. Every detail, every step felt like a celebration of tradition meeting elegance.
So grateful to be a part of this magical show and to bring his vision to life on stage. Thank you for trusting me with your creation, Kanak. Here's to many more walks, stories, and stunning ensembles!
